{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"accent-height","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/accent-height","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« 回到 SVG 属性指南首页</p>\n\n<p>此属性定义从原点到重点字符顶部的距离，通过字体坐标系内的距离测量。</p>\n\n<p>若未定义该属性，那么该属性就会被设置为<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/ascent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">ascent (en-US)</a></code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Categories</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#length\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#Number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Normative document</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/fonts.html#FontFaceElementAccentHeightAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p></p><dl>\n  <dt id=\"number_2\">&lt;number&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Real numbers are specified in one of two ways. When used in a stylesheet, a &lt;number&gt; is defined as follows:</p>\n    <pre class=\"notranslate\">number ::= integer\n            | [+-]? [0-9]* \".\" [0-9]+\n</pre>\n    <p>This syntax is the same as the definition in CSS (CSS2, section 4.3.1).</p>\n    <p>When used in an SVG attribute, a &lt;number&gt; is defined differently, to allow numbers with large magnitudes to be specified more concisely:</p>\n    <pre class=\"notranslate\">number ::= integer ([Ee] integer)?\n            | [+-]? [0-9]* \".\" [0-9]+ ([Ee] integer)?\n</pre>\n    <p>Within the SVG DOM, a &lt;number&gt; is represented as a float, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGNumber\"><code>SVGNumber</code></a> or a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedNumber\"><code>SVGAnimatedNumber</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following elements can use the <code>accent-height</code> attribute</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face\"><code>&lt;font-face&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"}],"summary":"« 回到 SVG 属性指南首页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"accent-height","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"accent-height","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"accent-height","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/accent-height","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/accent-height/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/accent-height","title":"accent-height"}],"pageTitle":"accent-height - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}